---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Navbar from '../components/navbar.astro';
import Team from '../components/team-bround.astro';
---

<Layout title="The Team | Society of Engineering">
	<main>
		<Navbar currPage='team' />
		<div>
			<Team />
		</div>
		<div>
			<table id="t1">
				<tbody>
					<tr>
						<td id="mem1"><h1>Kaustubh Lole</h1></td>
						<td><p>Hi, my name is Kaustubh Lole. I'm a junior at Amador Valley High School. Engineering has been my passion for a long time, and hopefully I can help teach all of you about the field I love. I'm in the PLTW Engineering pathway and have completed the second year of said pathway. Specifically, I am an aspiring mechanical engineer, and third year mechanical subdivision member of Amador Valley competitive robotics team, AVBotz.</p></td>
					</tr>
				</tbody>
			</table>
			<table id="t2">
				<tbody>
					<tr>
						<td><p>Hello, my name is Niel and I'm in 11th grade at Amador Valley High School. I love to code and create new things, which is why Iâ€™m doing engineering. I have completed the second year of advanced engineering at Amador. During my free time I have coded programs such as guessing games and chat bots and also completed a personal project, building a controllable car.</p></td>
						<td id="mem2"><h1>Niel Pal</h1></td>
					</tr>
				</tbody>
			</table>
		</div>
	</main>
</Layout>

<style>
	#t2 {
		margin-top: -2vw;
	}
	table {
		margin: 2vw;
	}
	#t1 {
		animation: flyin .5s ease-in-out;
		animation-delay: .6s;
		animation-fill-mode: forwards;
		opacity: 0;
	}
	#t2 {
		animation: flyin .4s ease-in-out;
		animation-delay: .8s;
		animation-fill-mode: forwards;
		opacity: 0;
	}
	th, td {
	border: .5px solid #fff;
	}
	h1 {
		font-weight: 750;
	}
	@media (max-width: 480px) {
		td {
			display: block;
			padding: 5vw;
		}
		p {
			font-size: 1em;
		}
		h1 {
			font-size: 3em;
		}
		#t2 tbody tr {
			display: flex;
			flex-direction: column-reverse;
		}
		#mem2 {
			padding: 10vw;
		}
	}
	@media (min-width: 480px) {
		p {
			font-size: 1.5em;
		}
		td {
			padding: 15vh;
		}
		h1 {
			font-size: 4em;
		}
		#mem2 {
			padding: 19vh;
		}
	}
	td {
		text-align: center;
	}

	#mem1 {
		background-image: url('/teammem1-bround.jpg');
	}
	#mem2 {
		background-image: url('/teammem2-bround.jpg');
	}
</style>